@host = http://localhost:5080

### --- Happy path -----------------------------------------------------------

### List users (paginated)
GET {{host}}/api/users?page=1&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### Get user by id
GET {{host}}/api/users/1
Accept: application/json

### Create a user
POST {{host}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Priya",
  "lastName": "Singh",
  "email": "priya.singh@techhive.example",
  "department": "HR",
  "role": "Recruiter"
}

### Update a user
PUT {{host}}/api/users/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Asha",
  "lastName": "Patel",
  "email": "asha.patel@techhive.example",
  "department": "HR",
  "role": "Director"
}

### Delete a user
DELETE {{host}}/api/users/2

### --- Edge cases for the debug pass ----------------------------------------

### Whitespace-only first name → 400 (caught by [NotWhitespace])
POST {{host}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "   ",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "blank.first@techhive.example",
  "department": "IT",
  "role": "Tester"
}

### Invalid email → 400 (caught by [EmailAddress])
POST {{host}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Bad",
  "lastName": "Email",
  "email": "not-an-email",
  "department": "IT",
  "role": "Tester"
}

### Duplicate email → 409 (uniqueness enforced atomically by service)
POST {{host}}/api/users
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Asha",
  "lastName": "Patel",
  "email": "asha.patel@techhive.example",
  "department": "HR",
  "role": "Manager"
}

### Get non-existent user → 404 ProblemDetails (no crash)
GET {{host}}/api/users/9999
Accept: application/json

### Bad id (negative) → 400 ProblemDetails
GET {{host}}/api/users/-1
Accept: application/json

### Page out of range → 400 ProblemDetails
GET {{host}}/api/users?page=0&pageSize=20
Accept: application/json

### Page size too large → 400 ProblemDetails (cap is 100)
GET {{host}}/api/users?page=1&pageSize=999
Accept: application/json

### Update non-existent user → 404 ProblemDetails
PUT {{host}}/api/users/9999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Ghost",
  "lastName": "User",
  "email": "ghost@techhive.example",
  "department": "IT",
  "role": "Engineer"
}

### Delete non-existent user → 404 ProblemDetails
DELETE {{host}}/api/users/9999
